data.description: This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath sits on a oversized lot on a quiet street.  Come and enjoy the covered porch, large rooms, and bright spaces.  Minutes to downtown, and all the shopping and entertainment your heart could desire in the trendy West 7th area, and the Historic Fort Worth Stockyards.  This quaint house is the perfect place for your family to call home.
